	(!HAVE_NETCONFIG_H && !HAVE_SYS_NETCONFIG_H)

	* aux/macros/check_nfs_prot_headers.m4: added new header for aix5.1+

	* buildall: fix 'buildall -b' on hpux9 and aix5.1

